Text: It is often hard to remember which of the many uploaders I need to thank for their selfless work, so i feel that when their are only a few providing something I watch regularlt that I now feel compelled to say THANK YOU, THANK YOUm THANK YOU. It doesn't hurt that I managed to remember on the occasion of the last show of the season. ;^)
Yo dude thank you for ur work week after week. I am very grateful for the opportunity to see one of my favourite shows. You da boss!
